          <h3>ETF Screener</h3>
          <p>Screen and compare ETFs across asset classes, expense ratios, yields, and fund providers.</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="disclaimer">Data represents approximate values as of Q1 2026. Market capitalizations and index weights are estimates based on public data. The S&amp;P 500 is maintained by S&amp;P Dow Jones Indices. Not investment advice.</div>
</div>

